// ArtifactLink
// Clickable link component for artifact notifications (documents and diagrams).
// Renders an icon, type label, and artifact name; clicking opens the artifact in the viewer.

FUNCTION getIconForArtifactType(type) -> ReactNode
  Returns an SVG icon matching the artifact type: document icon for documents, diagram icon for diagrams.

---

FUNCTION getTypeLabel(type) -> string
  Maps artifact type to a human-readable label ("Document", "Diagram").

---

FUNCTION handleClick(e)
  Prevents default link behavior.
  Calls onArtifactClick with the artifact data.

---

FUNCTION ArtifactLink(props) -> ReactNode                                 EXPORT
  Renders a button-style link with icon, type label, and artifact name.
  On click, calls handleClick to open the artifact.
